elements.name: Successfully create a new card application

steps.name: I navigate to the application creation page
I choose the option "individual" for the creation of the application
I choose the option "debit" for product type
I search the customer with CIF "10032034" and select it
I complete the Branch and Sales screen with "0001", "0001", "0001", "0001", "1100"
I go to the Review and Submit screen
I store the application id from the results table
I navigate to the approve card application page
I start the card application approve flow with the stored application id
I approve the card application on Level 2
I approve the card application on Level 3
